mas.maintenanceproxy.behavior

Class MonitorMaintenanceStatusBehavior

  • java.lang.Object
    • jade.core.behaviours.Behaviour
      • mas.maintenanceproxy.behavior.MonitorMaintenanceStatusBehavior
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MonitorMaintenanceStatusBehavior
extends jade.core.behaviours.Behaviour
    Author:
    Anand Prajapati

    Behavior to monitor status of the scheduled maintenance activity for machine. When maintenance agent generates and sends maintenance activity, it keeps track of whether maintenance is performed within the time frame or not through this behavior. If it is delayed then it first sends 2 warnings and 3rd time it cooperates with LSA to stop the machine.
